Author: mattchampionstan
Text: A big cycle of I Don’t Know What My Body Really Looks Like And At This Point I’m Too Afraid To Ask

Author: softcoffee
Text: This is me right now. I can tell my clothes fit so much better, and looser. I feel lighter and less bloated, but then I look at my stomach and my thighs and I'm just like "nope, time to fast for 24 hours and make sure I can't buy food."
